name: places/ChIJp-GkZosZ2jEReVkmfVrYymE/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQzX2NINkJREAE
text: {'text': "Recently I came across Yang Gallery to check out the yayoi kusama collection but was taken away with Wang Guoping's artwork. The use of AR in his art to allow viewers to interact with this art fascinates me! I scanned the QR code and it brings me to a website to scan the artwork. As someone that dabbles with art and culture, this is innovative use of technology with art. Really like it!!!", 'languageCode': 'en'}

name: places/ChIJp-GkZosZ2jEReVkmfVrYymE/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNIdTl5TWNnEAE
text: {'text': 'Beautiful space with a good range of artworks. Would highly recommend everyone to come by and view the current solo exhibition ‘Zen Meditation’ by Wang GuoPing. Be amazed by a wonderful music performance while viewing the artwork as well.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
